Class CSysDeliveryConfig

java.lang.Object
  de.systemagmbh.common.system.CSysDeliveryConfig
Deprecated. This class will not be replaced.

public class CSysDeliveryConfig
extends Object

The class CSysDeliveryConfig provides methods to set System properties from a Text file, from the jar or from Properties. It is useful to customize a default bundle of Components of SC2 without using long sequences with "-D"
